D

District - Class in fleetmanager.core
Object that represents a Berlin district Class variables: idx - an index to easily refer to a district, numScooters - number of scooters available in the district unitsWasted - if the FM attends this district, this is the number of extra scooter units that the FE's could have attended (but can't, as they can attend one district only)
